    <entry>
      <title>CSS教程-文本</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/30/CSS%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8E%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/30/CSS%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8E%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="CSS教程-文本"><a href="#CSS教程-文本" class="headerlink" title="CSS教程-文本"></a>CSS教程-文本</h1><h2 id="文本样式"><a href="#文本样式" class="headerlink" title="文本样式"></a>文本样式</h2><p>此部分及以后的部分讲的都是“属性”里可以填入的内容<br>CSS样式代码是有分类的，绝大部分的代码的格式都是如下：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">text-<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#000000</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>转换为中文就是：</p><blockquote><p>分类 - 项目：数值 ；</p></blockquote><p>今天讲的文本样式的分类是</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">text-</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>项目有</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">color</span>:#表示颜色的数值</span><br><span class="line">indent:数字em</span><br><span class="line">style:样式</span><br><span class="line">decoration:各种线</span><br><span class="line">align:对齐方式</span><br><span class="line">transform:默认大小写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>项目单独讲解如下：<br>decoration</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">underline //下划线</span><br><span class="line">overline //上划线</span><br><span class="line">line-through //删除线</span><br><span class="line">blink //闪烁</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>transform</p><pre><code class="CSS">c~ //首字母大写u~ //全大写l~ //全小写</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
